Abstract model. Corresponds to something that can digest features and produce targets, and also be stored as artifact.

class src.data_model.DraftInfo(draft_id: str, draft_name: str)¶

Bases: object

Info about draft. Draft is a platform-independent sketch of dataset; when implemented using a specific platform, it becomes a dataset implementation. For the time being, it’s fully untyped, that is its schema is not specified.
